1. Project Vision

The application is a digital platform aimed at:

Organizing affordable housing requests

Matching supply with demand based on location and budget

Reducing decision-making time

Enabling investors to fund projects quickly

Giving the company a clear view of the market before construction

The application is not just a listing site, but a tool for urban planning, marketing, and finance.

